data.description: So many treasures in this 4 BR, 2.5 Bath Home in Green Valley with a real Pool-size lot & paid off Solar!!. This home offers a step-down LR, Gas Fpl, Dining Room, & Family room off the extended kitchen. Brand new LG Upgraded fridge, Granite counters, dbl. oven 5 burner stove, SS appl. & a mineral RO sys. for drinking water + a whole house H2O to Go brand house water refiner in the 3 car garage. Tile floors in the 1st-floor entry, kitchen, hallway, and separate Laundry Rm. Upstairs we have 4 nice size BR's w/ the 2nd bath having dual sinks and a vanity. The Primary BR offers a walk-in closet w/ shelving, Bathtub, separate shower & dual sinks. XL yard has a stamped concrete patio & walkways, a lg. chain link fenced dog run, gazebo, plus a hot tub off to the side for privacy & e z access to the house, all with plenty of room for a pool. A firepit makes it a yard for year-round fun and cozy nights w/ smores. Plenty of restaurants, markets & shopping nearby. C in 3D, click the video icon.
